    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis has been maintained with essential subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing performance. Power is delivered through a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip. While the exterior shows minor signs of use, the drivetrain is robust, benefiting from a recent valve adjustment and refreshed cooling system components. It sits on staggered alloy wheels with a suspension setup that remains tight and communicative, offering the pure analog feedback expected of this iconic M-car.",
