    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera. This 996.2 generation features the 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power delivery through a 6-speed manual gearbox. Crucially, the IMS bearing has been upgraded to a permanent solution and the Rear Main Seal replaced, ensuring long-term drivetrain reliability. The suspension geometry remains precise, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers for improved transient response. While the finish shows minor patina from road use, the internal mechanicals are robust, featuring a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a high-revving soundtrack that defines the analog 911 experience. A purist\u2019s setup ready for the track or the open road.",
